msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"Et kraftfuldt, gratis donations- og betalingswidget, der giver dine "
"besøgende mulighed for at støtte dig via kreditkort eller kryptovaluta "
"(Quai). Ingen månedlige gebyrer, ingen tredjepartsabonnementer – kun din "
"kryptotask og gratis tjenester."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Nogle browsere blokerer tredjepartsskripter af hensyn til privatlivets fred."
" Denne proxy indlæser skripter via din egen server for at omgå disse "
"blokeringer."

